name: Iyana Halley🎞✨

social_posts.post_text: Focus on me 🥰🤍

One of my favorite places to be is at WORK. I have officially wrapped my last film of this year and I am so excited for the new year. Getting to be a working actress and working with people I admire will always make me feel a way that words can’t express. Im honored. Thank you GOD, always. Im excited for what the new year to come will bring but also living in the moment. I am overjoyed. 

To everyone who supports me, I love you. To every casting director, producer, network etc who takes a chance on me, I love you. To everyone on here who writes me kind messages, I love you.🤍.

Congrats to the cast and crew of IMANI! In theaters Jan 6th and streaming after that. 
#MannyHalleyProduction has done it again. @mannyhalley x @iamyolandahalley x @silenthustler and more. Starring @iambrittanyhall @krisdlofton @stephencbishop and more! Directed by @mikeho_ !

Can’t wait for y’all to see it! (No, I am not in this film but super excited abt it!)

Cheers to 2022. It was amazing. I’m extremely excited for 2023. Thank you God. ✨🫶🏾 and thank you to everyone who has been on this journey of me growing and evolving and figuring out this thing called LIFE. Love, always.

January 5th… BET+ new series! #ANGEL. Can’t wait for you guys to see me as ‘Sheree’. Make sure y’all tune in!✨

Happy National ME day! ♒️🎉🤎🎁It’s my birthday!!!!! Thank you God for allowing me to see another year. I am so blessed. So grateful. So happy. 

This year already feels different and I mean that in the best way possible. I am growing. I am evolving. I am working on becoming the best version of myself and Im on the right track. I pray this year is my best year thus far. I had so much fun at my birthday party!! 

Birthday queen! 🎂🎉🤍♒️

Guys, please mark your calendar March 4th @lifetimetv. This is a story that needs to be shared #HelpUsFindUs. 

Being an actress means the world to me but being able to use my platform to help share stories that really need to be told is something I always want to do. Once I read this script I knew I had to be apart of it. 

FACT: African Americans turn up missing at a startling pace and generally speaking take four times as long for law enforcement to locate than whites. 

I hope everyone tunes in and that this film truly brings AWARENESS. ✨ #blackandmissingfoundation 

Written by: @kalefutterman 
Starring: @garcelle x @officialtaylormosby x myself 
Directed by: @delmarwashington 
Special thank you to: @menuette.silver @jasonegenberg @lifetimetv and everyone else involved.

Ready to get into some trouble… Well, GOOD TROUBLE! Season 5 is back. I was especially excited at work bc this was my first time having my characters name on a chair for a TV show! It’s usually “guest cast” but Kendy has her own chair! I was smiling like a big kid. Tune in tonight. I love this show and sassy Miss Kendy! And as always, I had fun with my girls @candace.nicholas.lippman and @zuriadele . 🫶🏾💗💓
Directed by @marcofargnoli_dp 🎥

POV: You’re a young girl who loves watching TV. You dream of one day being on it…. But it sounds too much like a fantasy to ever really happen. Fast forward, years later… not only did you realize that dreams DO come true. But you get to really work with people you grew up watching. Isn’t that crazy?!! 

Thank you to the beautiful @garcelle for having me at you @realhousewivesofbhills screening. So glad the film is doing so well too! To everyone who supported it, THANK YOU!!!

We had a blast 🫶🏾🎥💕 oh and swipe all the way to the end to see miss FANCY😎❤️💫! My TV mom is not new to this lol. And an EP on this film! Talk about a BOSS❤️

Heavy on the Thank you GOD. Currently filming my newest film! And this one is taking me out of my comfort zone in the best ways possible! Growth all 2023 and beyond🤍

‘When the time is right, I, THE LORD, will make it happen’. Isaiah 60:22! 

I can’t wait to share details on this one. Having so much fun! It feels weird calling this WORK when it’s truly me living out my dreams. I’m so grateful. Stay tuned guys. This one is different for me. 😜😎🎉🤍💕🔪

Dreams DO come true.

“I see no competition bc my journey is one of a kind”. Truly🤍. I’ve wrapped a super fun movie that brought me out of my comfort zone in a lot of different ways. This film helped me grow in ways I didn’t realize I needed to. New Jersey was dope to shoot in! This cast and crew, wow. You guys treated me like family even though this was my first time meeting everyone. I’ll always be grateful for those who support me. Grateful. Blessed. Happy. Here are some cool BTS🥰. Jessica is brewing. Don’t worry, y’all can meet her soon😌 thank you God. appreciate everyone who made this possible for me. Thank you and love you guys

I had the honor of being one of the hosts alongside @romeomiller at @urbanfilmfestival in Miami! This meant the world to me. The kids there were such lights and full of energy. If i even inspired one person, then I know I’ve done my job🥹🫶🏾🤍. 

Romeo, I also learned so much from you. You dropped gems that both the audience and I soaked in. Loved hearing about your journey and faith. 

I believe God gave me a gift and I take pride in helping to inspire and motivate others. We chatted with some of the kids and gave them hugs and blessings and so much love. 

Thank you so much @marcomall for making this happen. What you’re doing is so important and needed. The way you are positively impacting our community doesn’t go unnoticed 🌹✨. I am inspired by you, truly.
